description:
Amazonia Raw Beauty Collagen Glow Peach Passionfruit contains 5000mg of highly bioavailable Type I & III hydrolysed marine collagen peptides and 100% RDI Vitamin C per serve to aid collagen production and support healthy hair, skin and nails.

With a delicious Peach Passionfruit flavour, this product features sustainably sourced, odourless and heat-stable Marine Collagen Peptides. Nourish your skin, hair and digestive systemwhile supporting your body's collagen levels.

Raw Beauty Collagen Glow Peach Passionfruit is delicious when added to water, smoothies, and bowls.



Amazonia is a global health company leading innovation with their range of Australian Certified Organic Raw Plant Protein and Supplements, Açaí, Tender Jack, and RawFIT Plant Protein and Supplements. Their plant-based products are made using real food ingredients – that means no GMOs, preservatives or synthetics. Amazonia prioritises ethical sourcing, organic farming, and sustainable agroforestry to nourish people and the planet.
